WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.125
Team Lime, I am very disappointed in you.

2
00:00:06.833 --> 00:00:10.416
I really thought we could
get somewhere with you - but we can't!

3
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Ah, I see it now,
your true colors.

4
00:00:18.125 --> 00:00:23.125
I don't understand... I've given everything,
to save this world.

5
00:00:23.125 --> 00:00:26.125
To save humanity... and now you're
treating me like this, yes?

6
00:00:28.625 --> 00:00:31.208
I don't understand what I've
done.

7
00:00:31.208 --> 00:00:33.708
What have I done so wrong, huh?

8
00:00:34.125 --> 00:00:35.750
You're too
radical.

9
00:00:35.750 --> 00:00:37.958
Too radical, you say.
Alright!

10
00:00:38.625 --> 00:00:42.375
I'll tell you what's going to happen - 
you'll go south sooner or later!

11
00:00:43.125 --> 00:00:46.125
I think you're going
south sooner!